{"type":"text","timestamp":1773482791355,"sessionID":"ses_3143289ffffebE5N0evuhJd5Hx","part":{"id":"prt_cebcfbba8002UW0KpxAJCxR0F4","sessionID":"ses_3143289ffffebE5N0evuhJd5Hx","messageID":"msg_cebcfb42c001KiaH4ACeIMSPWn","type":"text","text":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding. Let me implement the changes:\n\n1. **`monitor.ts`**: Make `MonitoredProcess.process` optional, add `reconnectProcess()`, update `isRunning()`, `remove()`, `killAll()`\n2. **`resume.ts`**: When an agent's PID is still alive during headless resume, call `monitor.reconnectProcess()` instead of just logging\n\nLet me start implementing:","time":{"start":1773482791354,"end":1773482791354}}}
