{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1773482957328,"sessionID":"ses_3143289ffffebE5N0evuhJd5Hx","part":{"id":"prt_cebd25a0e001Rb39SlRBMDu9LM","sessionID":"ses_3143289ffffebE5N0evuhJd5Hx","messageID":"msg_cebd24f39001exTjFoiR2Z3DSY","type":"step-start","snapshot":"ece90de063a772885e24c4f98598ca79312efb96"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1773482965517,"sessionID":"ses_3143289ffffebE5N0evuhJd5Hx","part":{"id":"prt_cebd25a0f001GbtLQpYevmNjWg","sessionID":"ses_3143289ffffebE5N0evuhJd5Hx","messageID":"msg_cebd24f39001exTjFoiR2Z3DSY","type":"text","text":"The interactive path doesn't use ProcessMonitor at all — it just launches mux sessions and prints a dashboard. That's fine. The `stillAlive` agents in interactive mode are already running in mux sessions, so they need no extra handling. The user can just `mux attach` to them. The interactive resume prints them correctly with the \"will reconnect\" message, which is accurate enough.\n\nBut wait — there's a subtlety. In the interactive path, the `stillAlive` agents are NOT in `toLaunchNow` (they weren't added to `toRelaunch`), so they won't be re-launched. They'll be left alone, which is correct. The only issue is the log message says \"will reconnect\" but in interactive mode there's no reconnection happening. Let me check if that matters...\n\nActually for the interactive path, the original message was \"leaving alone\" which was fine. My change to \"will reconnect\" is slightly misleading in interactive mode. Let me adjust the triage to say something more generic:","time":{"start":1773482965516,"end":1773482965516}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773482966087,"sessionID":"ses_3143289ffffebE5N0evuhJd5Hx","part":{"id":"prt_cebd270d6001kBS7ejwJ4RCBxN","sessionID":"ses_3143289ffffebE5N0evuhJd5Hx","messageID":"msg_cebd24f39001exTjFoiR2Z3DSY","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01L8aL16kWtbvm2S4ud6FynM","tool":"edit","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/wave-reconnect/src/commands/resume.ts","newString":"        if (agent.pid && isProcessRunning(agent.pid)) {\n          if (fmt === \"text\") console.log(`  ${agent.feature_id}: still running (PID ${agent.pid})`);\n          stillAlive.push(agent);","oldString":"        if (agent.pid && isProcessRunning(agent.pid)) {\n          if (fmt === \"text\") console.log(`  ${agent.feature_id}: still running (PID ${agent.pid}), will reconnect`);\n          stillAlive.push(agent);"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","title":"src/commands/resume.ts","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/wave-reconnect/src/lib/state.ts":[],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/wave-reconnect/src/lib/tui.ts":[{"range":{"start":{"line":29,"character":0},"end":{"line":29,"character":46}},"message":"'execSync' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"}],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/wave-reconnect/src/lib/monitor.ts":[],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/wave-reconnect/src/lib/launcher.ts":[{"range":{"start":{"line":65,"character":18},"end":{"line":65,"character":25}},"message":"'dirname' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"},{"range":{"start":{"line":122,"character":9},"end":{"line":122,"character":18}},"message":"'runSilent' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"}],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/wave-reconnect/src/commands/resume.ts":[{"range":{"start":{"line":36,