{"type":"text","timestamp":1773482998275,"sessionID":"ses_3143289ffffebE5N0evuhJd5Hx","part":{"id":"prt_cebd2ee7a0015VRdrfnnq3eM68","sessionID":"ses_3143289ffffebE5N0evuhJd5Hx","messageID":"msg_cebd2e578001yy7A3FO647fKpW","type":"text","text":"Both pass. Let me also check the launch.ts file. The same pattern exists there — in the polling loop, agents with alive PIDs that aren't in the monitor will trigger the \"PID dead\" path. But in `launch.ts`, agents are freshly launched, so they should always be in the monitor via `addProcess()`. Let me verify:","time":{"start":1773482998275,"end":1773482998275}}}
